{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":3651,"text":"Namaskar."}]},{"cues":[{"time":5810,"text":"I'm a movie star, I'm 51 years of age,"},{"time":9588,"text":"and I don't use Botox as yet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":11868,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":13108,"text":"So I'm clean, but I do behave like you saw\nlike a 21-year-old in my movies."},{"time":18468,"text":"Yeah, I do that."},{"time":19708,"text":"I sell dreams, and I peddle love\nto millions of people back home in India"},{"time":24628,"text":"who assume that I'm\nthe best lover in the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":26908,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":30068,"text":"If you don't tell anyone,\nI'm going to tell you I'm not,"},{"time":32748,"text":"but I never let that assumption go away."}]},{"cues":[{"time":34708,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":35748,"text":"I've also been made to understand"},{"time":37388,"text":"there are lots of you here\nwho haven't seen my work,"},{"time":39868,"text":"and I feel really sad for you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":41348,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":43788,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":48828,"text":"That doesn't take away from the fact\nthat I'm completely self-obsessed,"},{"time":52188,"text":"as a movie star should be."}]},{"cues":[{"time":53468,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":54548,"text":"That's when my friends,\nChris and Juliet called me here"},{"time":58188,"text":"to speak about the future \"you.\""},{"time":59778,"text":"Naturally, it follows I'm going\nto speak about the present me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":62738,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":67268,"text":"Because I truly believe\nthat humanity is a lot like me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":70068,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":71308,"text":"It is. It is."},{"time":72708,"text":"It's an aging movie star,"},{"time":75428,"text":"grappling with all\nthe newness around itself,"},{"time":78028,"text":"wondering whether\nit got it right in the first place,"},{"time":80708,"text":"and still trying to find a way"},{"time":82748,"text":"to keep on shining regardless."}]},{"cues":[{"time":85708,"text":"I was born in a refugee colony\nin the capital city of India, New Delhi."},{"time":89948,"text":"And my father was a freedom fighter."},{"time":92468,"text":"My mother was, well,\njust a fighter like mothers are."},{"time":97548,"text":"And much like the original homo sapiens,"},{"time":100588,"text":"we struggled to survive."},{"time":102908,"text":"When I was in my early 20s,"},{"time":105068,"text":"I lost both my parents,"},{"time":106828,"text":"which I must admit\nseems a bit careless of me now,"},{"time":110188,"text":"but --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":111508,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":117028,"text":"I do remember the night my father died,"},{"time":118948,"text":"and I remember the driver of a neighbor\nwho was driving us to the hospital."},{"time":123868,"text":"He mumbled something\nabout \"dead people don't tip so well\""},{"time":126708,"text":"and walked away into the dark."},{"time":128988,"text":"And I was only 14 then,"},{"time":130908,"text":"and I put my father's dead body\nin the back seat of the car,"},{"time":134388,"text":"and my mother besides me,"},{"time":135628,"text":"I started driving back\nfrom the hospital to the house."},{"time":138228,"text":"And in the middle of her quiet crying,\nmy mother looked at me and she said,"},{"time":141868,"text":"\"Son, when did you learn to drive?\""},{"time":146028,"text":"And I thought about it\nand realized, and I said to my mom,"},{"time":149308,"text":"\"Just now, Mom.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":150628,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":152908,"text":"So from that night onwards,"},{"time":154468,"text":"much akin to humanity in its adolescence,"},{"time":157188,"text":"I learned the crude tools of survival."},{"time":161148,"text":"And the framework of life was\nvery, very simple then, to be honest."},{"time":164828,"text":"You know, you just ate what you got"},{"time":167828,"text":"and did whatever you were told to do."},{"time":169668,"text":"I thought celiac was a vegetable,"},{"time":173028,"text":"and vegan, of course, was Mr. Spock's\nlost comrade in \"Star Trek.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":177588,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":178708,"text":"You married the first girl that you dated,"},{"time":181708,"text":"and you were a techie if you could fix\nthe carburetor in your car."},{"time":187108,"text":"I really thought that gay was\na sophisticated English word for happy."},{"time":191828,"text":"And Lesbian, of course, was the capital\nof Portugal, as you all know."}]},{"cues":[{"time":195108,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":196388,"text":"Where was I?"},{"time":200708,"text":"We relied on systems"},{"time":203068,"text":"created through the toil and sacrifice\nof generations before"},{"time":206788,"text":"to protect us,"},{"time":208268,"text":"and we felt that governments\nactually worked for our betterment."},{"time":211948,"text":"Science was simple and logical,"},{"time":213908,"text":"Apple was still then just a fruit"},{"time":217308,"text":"owned by Eve first and then Newton,"},{"time":219268,"text":"not by Steve Jobs, until then."},{"time":221628,"text":"And \"Eureka!\" was what you screamed"},{"time":223348,"text":"when you wanted\nto run naked on the streets."},{"time":226228,"text":"You went wherever life took you for work,"},{"time":229868,"text":"and people were mostly welcoming of you."},{"time":232588,"text":"Migration was a term then"},{"time":234588,"text":"still reserved for Siberian cranes,\nnot human beings."},{"time":237988,"text":"Most importantly, you were who you were"},{"time":240868,"text":"and you said what you thought."}]},{"cues":[{"time":243388,"text":"Then in my late 20s,"},{"time":244668,"text":"I shifted to the sprawling\nmetropolis of Mumbai,"},{"time":248428,"text":"and my framework,"},{"time":249788,"text":"like the newly industrialized\naspirational humanity,"},{"time":253108,"text":"began to alter."},{"time":254948,"text":"In the urban rush for a new,\nmore embellished survival,"},{"time":258387,"text":"things started to look a little different."},{"time":260428,"text":"I met people who had descended\nfrom all over the world,"},{"time":264148,"text":"faces, races, genders, money-lenders."},{"time":267388,"text":"Definitions became more and more fluid."},{"time":270268,"text":"Work began to define you at that time"},{"time":273388,"text":"in an overwhelmingly equalizing manner,"},{"time":276068,"text":"and all the systems\nstarted to feel less reliable to me,"},{"time":278948,"text":"almost too thick to hold on"},{"time":282108,"text":"to the diversity of mankind"},{"time":284108,"text":"and the human need to progress and grow."},{"time":287508,"text":"Ideas were flowing\nwith more freedom and speed."},{"time":291388,"text":"And I experienced the miracle\nof human innovation and cooperation,"},{"time":296748,"text":"and my own creativity,"},{"time":298188,"text":"when supported by the resourcefulness\nof this collective endeavor,"},{"time":302708,"text":"catapulted me into superstardom."}]},{"cues":[{"time":305148,"text":"I started to feel that I had arrived,"},{"time":307588,"text":"and generally, by the time I was 40,\nI was really, really flying."},{"time":311108,"text":"I was all over the place."},{"time":312388,"text":"You know? I'd done 50 films by then"},{"time":314428,"text":"and 200 songs,"},{"time":316788,"text":"and I'd been knighted by the Malaysians."},{"time":319068,"text":"I had been given the highest civil honor\nby the French government,"},{"time":322388,"text":"the title of which for the life of me\nI can't pronounce even until now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":325748,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":326828,"text":"I'm sorry, France, and thank you,\nFrance, for doing that."},{"time":330268,"text":"But much bigger than that,\nI got to meet Angelina Jolie --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":333628,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":336388,"text":"for two and a half seconds."}]},{"cues":[{"time":337908,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":339228,"text":"And I'm sure she also remembers\nthat encounter somewhere."},{"time":341948,"text":"OK, maybe not."},{"time":343188,"text":"And I sat next to Hannah Montana\non a round dinner table"},{"time":346748,"text":"with her back towards me most of the time."},{"time":349588,"text":"Like I said, I was flying,\nfrom Miley to Jolie,"},{"time":352748,"text":"and humanity was soaring with me."},{"time":356028,"text":"We were both pretty much\nflying off the handle, actually."}]},{"cues":[{"time":359268,"text":"And then you all know what happened."},{"time":361508,"text":"The internet happened."},{"time":363748,"text":"I was in my late 40s,"},{"time":365708,"text":"and I started tweeting\nlike a canary in a birdcage"},{"time":369268,"text":"and assuming that, you know,\npeople who peered into my world"},{"time":372268,"text":"would admire it"},{"time":373548,"text":"for the miracle I believed it to be."},{"time":375668,"text":"But something else\nawaited me and humanity."},{"time":378748,"text":"You know, we had expected\nan expansion of ideas and dreams"},{"time":383668,"text":"with the enhanced\nconnectivity of the world."},{"time":387028,"text":"We had not bargained\nfor the village-like enclosure of thought,"},{"time":394708,"text":"of judgment, of definition"},{"time":396748,"text":"that flowed from the same place"},{"time":398908,"text":"that freedom and revolution\nwas taking place in."},{"time":402508,"text":"Everything I said took a new meaning."},{"time":404908,"text":"Everything I did -- good, bad, ugly --"},{"time":407828,"text":"was there for the world\nto comment upon and judge."},{"time":411188,"text":"As a matter of fact,\neverything I didn't say or do also"},{"time":414588,"text":"met with the same fate."}]},{"cues":[{"time":416708,"text":"Four years ago,"},{"time":418948,"text":"my lovely wife Gauri and me\ndecided to have a third child."},{"time":423988,"text":"It was claimed on the net"},{"time":426788,"text":"that he was the love child"},{"time":428908,"text":"of our first child"},{"time":430708,"text":"who was 15 years old."},{"time":432788,"text":"Apparently, he had sown\nhis wild oats with a girl"},{"time":435908,"text":"while driving her car in Romania."},{"time":438988,"text":"And yeah, there was\na fake video to go with it."},{"time":441628,"text":"And we were so disturbed as a family."},{"time":443468,"text":"My son, who is 19 now,"},{"time":444748,"text":"even now when you say \"hello\" to him,"},{"time":446588,"text":"he just turns around and says,"},{"time":448068,"text":"\"But bro, I didn't even have\na European driving license.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":450788,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":453268,"text":"Yeah."},{"time":455028,"text":"In this new world,"},{"time":456748,"text":"slowly, reality became virtual\nand virtual became real,"},{"time":460148,"text":"and I started to feel"},{"time":461828,"text":"that I could not be who I wanted to be\nor say what I actually thought,"},{"time":465388,"text":"and humanity at this time"},{"time":468308,"text":"completely identified with me."},{"time":470268,"text":"I think both of us\nwere going through our midlife crisis,"},{"time":474308,"text":"and humanity, like me,\nwas becoming an overexposed prima donna."},{"time":478428,"text":"I started to sell everything,"},{"time":480148,"text":"from hair oil to diesel generators."},{"time":483068,"text":"Humanity was buying everything"},{"time":485108,"text":"from crude oil to nuclear reactors."},{"time":487508,"text":"You know, I even tried\nto get into a skintight superhero suit"},{"time":491508,"text":"to reinvent myself."},{"time":494268,"text":"I must admit I failed miserably."},{"time":497028,"text":"And just an aside I want to say\non behalf of all the Batmen, Spider-Men"},{"time":502068,"text":"and Supermen of the world,"},{"time":504188,"text":"you have to commend them,"},{"time":506068,"text":"because it really hurts in the crotch,\nthat superhero suit."}]},{"cues":[{"time":508868,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":509948,"text":"Yeah, I'm being honest.\nI need to tell you this here."},{"time":513948,"text":"Really."},{"time":515188,"text":"And accidentally, I happened\nto even invent a new dance form"},{"time":518748,"text":"which I didn't realize,\nand it became a rage."},{"time":520907,"text":"So if it's all right,"},{"time":522147,"text":"and you've seen a bit of me,\nso I'm quite shameless, I'll show you."},{"time":525348,"text":"It was called the Lungi dance."},{"time":526828,"text":"So if it's all right, I'll just show you.\nI'm talented otherwise."}]},{"cues":[{"time":529948,"text":"(Cheers)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":531188,"text":"So it went something like this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":533868,"text":"Lungi dance. Lungi dance.\nLungi dance. Lungi dance."},{"time":536308,"text":"Lungi dance. Lungi dance.\nLungi dance. Lungi dance."},{"time":538748,"text":"Lungi dance. Lungi dance.\nLungi dance. Lungi."}]},{"cues":[{"time":541428,"text":"That's it. It became a rage."}]},{"cues":[{"time":543108,"text":"(Cheers)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":544428,"text":"It really did."},{"time":547948,"text":"Like you notice, nobody could make\nany sense of what was happening except me,"},{"time":551628,"text":"and I didn't give a damn, really,"},{"time":553268,"text":"because the whole world,\nand whole humanity,"},{"time":555508,"text":"seemed as confused and lost as I was."},{"time":558548,"text":"I didn't give up then."},{"time":559828,"text":"I even tried to reconstruct\nmy identity on the social media"},{"time":562628,"text":"like everyone else does."},{"time":563908,"text":"I thought if I put on\nphilosophical tweets out there"},{"time":566668,"text":"people will think I'm with it,"},{"time":568268,"text":"but some of the responses I got\nfrom those tweets"},{"time":570868,"text":"were extremely confusing acronyms\nwhich I didn't understand. You know?"},{"time":574228,"text":"ROFL, LOL."},{"time":576308,"text":"\"Adidas,\" somebody wrote back\nto one of my more thought-provoking tweets"},{"time":580628,"text":"and I was wondering\nwhy would you name a sneaker,"},{"time":582988,"text":"I mean, why would you write back\nthe name of a sneaker to me?"},{"time":585908,"text":"And I asked my 16-year-old daughter,\nand she enlightened me."},{"time":588788,"text":"\"Adidas\" now means\n\"All day I dream about sex.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":592308,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":594588,"text":"Really."},{"time":595908,"text":"I didn't know if you know that."},{"time":597428,"text":"So I wrote back,\n\"WTF\" in bold to Mr. Adidas,"},{"time":602028,"text":"thanking secretly that some acronyms\nand things won't change at all."},{"time":607188,"text":"WTF."}]},{"cues":[{"time":610188,"text":"But here we are."},{"time":612388,"text":"I am 51 years old, like I told you,"},{"time":614108,"text":"and mind-numbing acronyms notwithstanding,"},{"time":617708,"text":"I just want to tell you"},{"time":619028,"text":"if there has been a momentous time\nfor humanity to exist,"},{"time":622268,"text":"it is now,"},{"time":623908,"text":"because the present you is brave."},{"time":627308,"text":"The present you is hopeful."},{"time":628668,"text":"The present you\nis innovative and resourceful,"},{"time":631988,"text":"and of course, the present you\nis annoyingly indefinable."},{"time":636308,"text":"And in this spell-binding,"},{"time":638788,"text":"imperfect moment of existence,"},{"time":640748,"text":"feeling a little brave\njust before I came here,"},{"time":643348,"text":"I decided to take\na good, hard look at my face."},{"time":647668,"text":"And I realized that I'm beginning\nto look more and more"},{"time":651348,"text":"like the wax statue of me\nat Madame Tussaud's."}]},{"cues":[{"time":653788,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":656068,"text":"Yeah, and in that moment of realization,"},{"time":658588,"text":"I asked the most central\nand pertinent question to humanity and me:"},{"time":664268,"text":"Do I need to fix my face?"},{"time":667388,"text":"Really. I'm an actor, like I told you,"},{"time":670748,"text":"a modern expression of human creativity."},{"time":674148,"text":"The land I come from"},{"time":675708,"text":"is the source of inexplicable\nbut very simple spirituality."},{"time":681868,"text":"In its immense generosity,"},{"time":684388,"text":"India decided somehow"},{"time":687148,"text":"that I, the Muslim son\nof a broke freedom fighter"},{"time":691148,"text":"who accidentally ventured\ninto the business of selling dreams,"},{"time":695908,"text":"should become its king of romance,"},{"time":700828,"text":"the \"Badhshah of Bollywood,\""},{"time":703868,"text":"the greatest lover\nthe country has ever seen ..."},{"time":707508,"text":"with this face."},{"time":709228,"text":"Yeah."}]},{"cues":[{"time":710468,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":711588,"text":"Which has alternately\nbeen described as ugly, unconventional,"},{"time":714508,"text":"and strangely, not chocolatey enough."}]},{"cues":[{"time":716348,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":721668,"text":"The people of this ancient land"},{"time":724028,"text":"embraced me in their limitless love,"},{"time":726468,"text":"and I've learned from these people"},{"time":729028,"text":"that neither power nor poverty"},{"time":732228,"text":"can make your life more magical"},{"time":733948,"text":"or less tortuous."},{"time":735948,"text":"I've learned from the people of my country"},{"time":738588,"text":"that the dignity of a life,"},{"time":740708,"text":"a human being, a culture,\na religion, a country"},{"time":745348,"text":"actually resides in its ability"},{"time":748388,"text":"for grace and compassion."},{"time":750508,"text":"I've learned that whatever moves you,"},{"time":753268,"text":"whatever urges you to create, to build,"},{"time":755988,"text":"whatever keeps you from failing,"},{"time":757668,"text":"whatever helps you survive,"},{"time":759948,"text":"is perhaps the oldest and the simplest\nemotion known to mankind,"},{"time":764348,"text":"and that is love."},{"time":767508,"text":"A mystic poet from my land famously wrote,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":770428,"text":"(Recites poem in Hindi)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":781108,"text":"(Poem ends)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":782788,"text":"Which loosely translates\ninto that whatever --"},{"time":785388,"text":"yeah, if you know Hindi,\nplease clap, yeah."}]},{"cues":[{"time":787488,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":788948,"text":"It's very difficult to remember."},{"time":791428,"text":"Which loosely translates\ninto actually saying"},{"time":794028,"text":"that all the books of knowledge\nthat you might read"},{"time":796508,"text":"and then go ahead\nand impart your knowledge"},{"time":799428,"text":"through innovation,\nthrough creativity, through technology,"},{"time":802788,"text":"but mankind will never be\nthe wiser about its future"},{"time":805948,"text":"unless it is coupled with a sense of love\nand compassion for their fellow beings."},{"time":812708,"text":"The two and a half alphabets\nwhich form the word \"प्रेम,\""},{"time":816308,"text":"which means \"love,\""},{"time":817748,"text":"if you are able to understand that"},{"time":819668,"text":"and practice it,"},{"time":821268,"text":"that itself is enough\nto enlighten mankind."},{"time":825308,"text":"So I truly believe the future \"you\""},{"time":828148,"text":"has to be a you that loves."},{"time":830628,"text":"Otherwise it will cease to flourish."},{"time":833628,"text":"It will perish in its own self-absorption."}]},{"cues":[{"time":838508,"text":"So you may use your power"},{"time":840668,"text":"to build walls"},{"time":842388,"text":"and keep people outside,"},{"time":845148,"text":"or you may use it to break barriers\nand welcome them in."},{"time":850028,"text":"You may use your faith"},{"time":851828,"text":"to make people afraid"},{"time":854348,"text":"and terrify them into submission,"},{"time":857228,"text":"or you can use it\nto give courage to people"},{"time":859708,"text":"so they rise to the greatest\nheights of enlightenment."},{"time":863468,"text":"You can use your energy"},{"time":865428,"text":"to build nuclear bombs\nand spread the darkness of destruction,"},{"time":868788,"text":"or you can use it to spread\nthe joy of light to millions."},{"time":873548,"text":"You may filthy up the oceans callously\nand cut down all the forests."},{"time":877588,"text":"You can destroy the ecology,"},{"time":880028,"text":"or turn to them with love"},{"time":882228,"text":"and regenerate life\nfrom the waters and trees."},{"time":885468,"text":"You may land on Mars"},{"time":887268,"text":"and build armed citadels,"},{"time":890668,"text":"or you may look for life-forms and species\nto learn from and respect."},{"time":896428,"text":"And you can use\nall the moneys we all have earned"},{"time":900188,"text":"to wage futile wars"},{"time":903108,"text":"and give guns in the hands\nof little children"},{"time":906028,"text":"to kill each other with,"},{"time":908468,"text":"or you can use it"},{"time":910428,"text":"to make more food"},{"time":912188,"text":"to fill their stomachs with."}]},{"cues":[{"time":914668,"text":"My country has taught me"},{"time":916348,"text":"the capacity for a human being to love\nis akin to godliness."},{"time":921748,"text":"It shines forth in a world"},{"time":926228,"text":"which civilization, I think,\nalready has tampered too much with."},{"time":932668,"text":"In the last few days,\nthe talks here, the wonderful people"},{"time":935428,"text":"coming and showing their talent,"},{"time":937188,"text":"talking about individual achievements,\nthe innovation, the technology,"},{"time":940548,"text":"the sciences, the knowledge\nwe are gaining by being here"},{"time":943908,"text":"in the presence of TED Talks\nand all of you"},{"time":946708,"text":"are reasons enough\nfor us to celebrate the future \"us.\""},{"time":949748,"text":"But within that celebration"},{"time":952388,"text":"the quest to cultivate\nour capacity for love and compassion"},{"time":957388,"text":"has to assert itself,\nhas to assert itself,"},{"time":961148,"text":"just as equally."}]},{"cues":[{"time":963948,"text":"So I believe the future \"you\""},{"time":967028,"text":"is an infinite you."},{"time":969228,"text":"It's called a chakra\nin India, like a circle."},{"time":972828,"text":"It ends where it begins from\nto complete itself."},{"time":977068,"text":"A you that perceives\ntime and space differently"},{"time":980788,"text":"understands both"},{"time":984868,"text":"your unimaginable"},{"time":989508,"text":"and fantastic importance"},{"time":991948,"text":"and your complete unimportance\nin the larger context of the universe."},{"time":998668,"text":"A you that returns back"},{"time":1000948,"text":"to the original innocence of humanity,"},{"time":1002828,"text":"which loves from the purity of heart,"},{"time":1005748,"text":"which sees from the eyes of truth,"},{"time":1009308,"text":"which dreams from the clarity\nof an untampered mind."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1016268,"text":"The future \"you\" has to be"},{"time":1018548,"text":"like an aging movie star"},{"time":1021068,"text":"who has been made to believe\nthat there is a possibility"},{"time":1024028,"text":"of a world which is completely,"},{"time":1026828,"text":"wholly, self-obsessively"},{"time":1029868,"text":"in love with itself."},{"time":1031947,"text":"A world -- really, it has to be a you"},{"time":1035268,"text":"to create a world"},{"time":1037227,"text":"which is its own best lover."},{"time":1040028,"text":"That I believe, ladies and gentlemen,"},{"time":1041868,"text":"should be the future \"you.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1043427,"text":"Thank you very much."},{"time":1044908,"text":"Shukriya."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1046148,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1048308,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1049548,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1052508,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1053788,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}